{"story":{"group_1":[{"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","nameNarration":"月咲","narration":"之后，在和月夜的交流中，@我知道了妈妈是水名的人","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"知道了月夜的外婆@叫她不要到工匠区来"},{"narration":"我想她肯定是不想让我们@发现自己还有双胞胎姐妹"},{"narration":"在聊了很久之后，@我和月夜都开始止不住地抱怨起来"},{"bg":"bg_adv_12052.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"月夜","nameRight":"月咲","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"很不讲道理吧！？@洗衣做饭打扫管理家用。"},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"只要能想到的家务都得做！"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"而且大家完全都不来帮忙！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"当然，我是很尊敬爸爸啦！"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"他的工作很辛苦，也很重要，@而且还要成为学徒的支柱。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"但这是两码事吧！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":300}],"textRight":"整天说这是女人的工作，@他是生错时代了吧！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"是啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"弄得我放学后@几乎都没法出去玩。"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":200}],"textRight":"就算找身边的人商量，@他们也无法理解。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"我从一开始就知道@自己家很奇怪了。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"你明白吗！？@这种痛苦和空虚！"},{"chara":[{"id":101801,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"我当然明白！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"没想到我们的境遇都这么相似，@简直就像是双胞胎一样呢。"},{"nameNarration":"月咲","narration":"跟温柔颔首的月夜聊天，@总觉得不同于和学校里的那些人交谈，@我能够切实地传达出自己的情感","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"虽然不清楚原因，@但我心里觉得，@或许因为我们是双胞胎吧"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"天音","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101801}],"textLeft":"真想下次能再见到你，@和你说说话。"},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"别叫得这么生分啦。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"诶？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"好吗，月夜。"},{"chara":[{"id":101801}],"textLeft":"啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"好的，月咲！"},{"nameNarration":"月咲","narration":"我们只用一天的时间就变得亲密起来，@交换了联络方式，@并约好下次再见","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21173.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"当然，我怕输入真名被爸爸发现，@所以就改成了其他名字"},{"narration":"就和笛子一样，合而为一的——"},{"narration":"“●”模样的满月印记"},{"bgm":"stop","narration":"但是，亲密的时光@并没有延续太久……","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg"},{"narration":"甚至让我许下了那样的愿望","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1019_00_04","textHome":"爸爸如果能告诉我就好了……"}],"nameCenter":"月咲","textCenter":"要是爸爸早点告诉我就好了……","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":300}]},{"chara":[{"id":101901}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}